# ğŸ¬ X-Tube: A MERN-Based YouTube Clone

## ğŸš€ Overview
X-Tube is a **YouTube-like video-sharing platform** built using the **MERN (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js) stack**. This platform enables users to **upload, share, like, dislike, comment on videos, and download** content. It also features a **real-time chat system** powered by **Socket.io**.

